      "description": "Hey friends! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the crazy dealership sticker shock, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
