    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained dual-VANOS system. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. All critical maintenance milestones have been addressed, including documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the telepathic handling characteristics these chassis are renowned for. Free from any fluid leaks or electronic faults, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a concours-level icon with unparalleled mechanical transparency.",
